{
  "event_id": "wanxing_h1",
  "npc_id": "wanxing",
  "title": "春季夜晚在观星台",
  "description": "与晚星在春季夜晚的观星台相遇",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "wanxing_h1_start",
      "speaker": "晚星",
      "text": "$[PLAYER_NAME]……今晚的星星好亮。你也来看星星吗？",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_1",
          "text": "是。我听说这里的星空很美。",
          "next_node_id": "wanxing_h1_beautiful"
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_2",
          "text": "你经常一个人在这里看星星吗？",
          "next_node_id": "wanxing_h1_alone"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "wanxing_h1_beautiful",
      "speaker": "晚星",
      "text": "云海的星空，是世界上最安静的地方。每颗星星都有自己的故事……你想听吗？",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_listen",
          "text": "当然想听。",
          "next_node_id": "wanxing_h1_story"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "wanxing_h1_alone",
      "speaker": "晚星",
      "text": "……嗯。以前是一个人。但今晚，有你。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_company",
          "text": "以后我陪你一起看。",
          "next_node_id": "wanxing_h1_promise"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "wanxing_h1_story",
      "speaker": "晚星",
      "text": "那颗是北辰星，无论季节如何变换，它永远指向北方……就像有些东西，永远不会改变。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_meaning",
          "text": "就像你吗？",
          "next_node_id": "wanxing_h1_meaning"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "wanxing_h1_promise",
      "speaker": "晚星",
      "text": "$[PLAYER_NAME]……你知道吗？星星最怕的不是云遮，而是没有人一起看。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_end",
          "text": "我记住了。",
          "next_node_id": "wanxing_h1_end"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "wanxing_h1_meaning",
      "speaker": "晚星",
      "text": "……也许吧。但今晚，我更想说——星星找到了新的故事。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_end",
          "text": "我很荣幸能听你讲。",
          "next_node_id": "wanxing_h1_end"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "wanxing_h1_end",
      "speaker": "晚星",
      "text": "今晚的星星，我会记住的。因为……有你在的星空，是不一样的。",
      "is_ending": true,
      "reward_favor": 10
    }
  ]
}
